Installation:
- With version 1.6.5 of Git and later, you can use:
	git clone --recursive https://github.com/berkedel/dotvim.git ~/.vim
- For older Git version, just use:
    git clone https://github.com/berkedel/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule update --init

Create symlinks:
	ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
	ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
